WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:00.031 --> 00:00:03.179
<i>Previously on</i>  aMC's 
Better Call Saul...

2
00:00:03.352 --> 00:00:04.898
Should I settle?

3
00:00:11.477 --> 00:00:13.007
Hector Salamanca.

4
00:00:13.179 --> 00:00:15.265
- Turn the lights on.
- I'm back to normal.

5
00:00:15.335 --> 00:00:17.421
You'd rather tear down
HHM than retire.

6
00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:19.859
You think I'm trouble now?
Imagine me as your enemy.

7
00:00:19.931 --> 00:00:22.210
(Kim:) It's a new client. and
if I mess this up. it's a<i> former</i> client.

8
00:00:22.291 --> 00:00:25.609
Sandpiper is settling.
This is the solution to everything!

9
00:00:25.710 --> 00:00:27.445
I'll be back in a few hours.

10
00:00:27.547 --> 00:00:30.039
- [Air bag explodes]
- [Gasps]

11
00:00:33.203 --> 00:00:36.179
(Young Chuck:) "It was very still
except for the tree-toads

12
00:00:36.304 --> 00:00:40.097
and the frogs in the brook
peeping mournfully.

13
00:00:40.487 --> 00:00:42.408
and every little while

14
00:00:42.783 --> 00:00:45.752
Mabel could hear strange
rustlings in the leaves.

15
00:00:46.046 --> 00:00:48.541
[Dog barking in distance] She
tried to remember the way home.

16
00:00:48.811 --> 00:00:50.352
but the woods
looked so different now

17
00:00:50.492 --> 00:00:53.260
that she couldn't think
which way to go.

18
00:00:53.618 --> 00:00:55.850
She began to be frightened.

19
00:00:56.082 --> 00:00:57.949
'What's that?' Said Mabel.

20
00:00:58.038 --> 00:01:00.354
'Oh. I'm...
I'm so frightened!'

21
00:01:00.641 --> 00:01:03.501
in a minute or two
she heard the howl again...

22
00:01:03.802 --> 00:01:06.662
'o-o-o-w!'...

23
00:01:06.963 --> 00:01:09.761
a long. wild cry.

24
00:01:10.620 --> 00:01:14.673
She began to run. but the poor
thing had lost her way."

25
00:01:14.940 --> 00:01:16.960
Is she gonna be okay?

26
00:01:17.158 --> 00:01:19.926
She'll be fine. Jimmy.
How do you know?

27
00:01:20.145 --> 00:01:23.015
Just listen.
You'll see.

28
00:01:23.332 --> 00:01:25.506
[Gas hissing]

29
00:01:25.696 --> 00:01:27.726
"It was so dark
that she stumbled

30
00:01:27.835 --> 00:01:30.065
over the bushes and the roots
of the trees..."

