the chicken trucks.

716
00:42:00.730 --> 00:42:02.284
That is final.

717
00:42:02.332 --> 00:42:05.492
But you must understand
this is for efficiency only...

718
00:42:05.613 --> 00:42:09.123
there's no disrespect
to you or your family.

719
00:42:10.459 --> 00:42:12.394
What's he doing here?

720
00:42:12.614 --> 00:42:14.944
The boss wants you
to settle this.

721
00:42:16.077 --> 00:42:18.877
I settle it right now. okay?

722
00:42:19.268 --> 00:42:20.799
[Sighs]
You have to work together.

723
00:42:20.889 --> 00:42:22.369
It's what the boss wants.

724
00:42:22.489 --> 00:42:25.658
The boss can suck me.

725
