Me and my family?

729
00:42:34.587 --> 00:42:36.917
We built this whole business.

730
00:42:37.072 --> 00:42:38.369
We all did.
Together.

731
00:42:38.432 --> 00:42:41.071
No. no!
Salamanca did!

732
00:42:41.206 --> 00:42:42.932
Salamanca money!

733
00:42:43.011 --> 00:42:44.705
Salamanca blood!

734
00:42:44.813 --> 00:42:45.899
You have to calm down.

735
00:42:45.947 --> 00:42:47.948
That hacienda!
I paid for it.

736
00:42:48.016 --> 00:42:49.803
And you treat us like dogs!

737
00:42:49.851 --> 00:42:51.588
Hector. this isn't personal...

738
00:42:51.737 --> 00:42:54.619
It is!
It is personal...!

739
