775
00:44:48.400 --> 00:44:50.727
No complaints.
Join me.

776
00:44:51.157 --> 00:44:52.211
[Sighs]

777
00:44:52.259 --> 00:44:54.360
Oh... Dip...
dip it in the sauce.

778
00:44:54.680 --> 00:44:56.039
Seems like overkill.

779
00:44:56.132 --> 00:44:57.578
Trust me.

780
00:44:58.324 --> 00:45:00.196
[Crunching]

781
00:45:00.289 --> 00:45:01.782
Mmm.

782
00:45:02.332 --> 00:45:03.477
So what's next?

783
00:45:03.614 --> 00:45:05.399
Uh. monty python.

784
00:45:05.629 --> 00:45:06.836
Solid choice.

785
00:45:06.884 --> 00:45:10.336
Or... We could just watch
"to kill a mockingbird" again.

786
00:45:10.540 --> 00:45:12.742
Again? Yeah. I watched
it this morning.

787
00:45:13.010 --> 00:45:14.641
It was my favorite
when I was a kid.

788
00:45:14.735 --> 00:45:16.008
I loved Atticus Finch.

789
00:45:16.108 --> 00:45:18.408
All the girls were in love
with Gregory peck.

790
00:45:18.482 --> 00:45:20.774
No.
I wasn't<i> in</i> love with him.

791
00:45:21.122 --> 00:45:24.344
Well. a little. But. no.
I wanted to<i> be</i> him.

792
00:45:24.586 --> 00:45:26.946
Fight the good fight.
Change the world.

793
00:45:27.190 --> 00:45:29.274
Yeah.
Didn't you?

794
00:45:30.774 --> 00:45:34.180
That was more Chuck's thing.

795
00:45:35.129 --> 00:45:37.688
But. I mean. the good news is
you made it!

796
00:45:37.891 --> 00:45:39.555
Oh. yeah. Yeah.
I am.

797
00:45:39.648 --> 00:45:43.148
I'm changing the world
by helping a mid-size local bank

798
00:45:43.206 --> 00:45:45.008
