regional bank.

799
00:45:45.242 --> 00:45:46.942
Yay me.

800
00:45:50.144 --> 00:45:52.938
So... No luck
with Ms. Landry?

801
00:45:53.350 --> 00:45:56.266
No. Shoot.
That bridge is burned.

802
00:45:56.326 --> 00:45:57.339
Ashes.

803
00:45:57.453 --> 00:45:58.907
It's that bad?
[Sighs]

804
00:45:59.122 --> 00:46:01.508
T-there's no putting that genie
back in the bottle.

805
00:46:01.625 --> 00:46:03.727
And I've tried everything.

806
00:46:03.899 --> 00:46:06.164
I sent muffin baskets
to the gals.

807
00:46:06.274 --> 00:46:08.096
I signed them from her.
Nice.

808
00:46:08.227 --> 00:46:09.516
They saw right through it.

809
00:46:09.599 --> 00:46:11.269
"Oh. Jimmy. you're too nice.

810
00:46:11.344 --> 00:46:13.000
Jimmy.
she doesn't deserve you."

811
00:46:13.103 --> 00:46:15.086
The more I try to make them
like her again.

812
00:46:15.188 --> 00:46:18.094
the more they end up
lovin' me instead.

813
00:46:18.546 --> 00:46:22.032
Wow. Well... Sounds like you've
exhausted all your options...

814
00:46:22.080 --> 00:46:23.850
I mean. if muffin baskets
Don't solve it...

815
00:46:23.905 --> 00:46:25.750
I Don't know what else to do.

816
00:46:25.894 --> 00:46:28.203
I'm not good at building shit.
you know?

817
00:46:28.251 --> 00:46:30.899
I'm excellent
at tearing it down.

818
00:46:32.078 --> 00:46:33.984
[Sighs]

819
00:46:35.152 --> 00:46:37.672
[Sighs]
Oh. rookie move.

820
00:46:37.891 --> 00:46:40.016
What... the...
[Grunts]

821
