It's already cheese.
It's cheese on cheese.

822
00:46:42.805 --> 00:46:44.400
See?
[Crunching]

823
00:46:44.477 --> 00:46:48.040
You know. sometimes. you got to
play to your strengths.

824
00:46:48.383 --> 00:46:50.063
You should stitch that
on a pillow.

825
00:46:50.129 --> 00:46:52.429
Oh. I will.
All right. Screw it.

826
00:46:52.828 --> 00:46:55.142
"Mockingbird" encore. it is.

827
00:46:58.071 --> 00:46:59.671
[Sighs]

828
00:47:00.899 --> 00:47:02.782
No.

829
00:47:03.344 --> 00:47:05.008
Oh. shit.

830
00:47:05.082 --> 00:47:06.312
What?
What is it?

831
00:47:06.442 --> 00:47:09.758
[Chuckles]
Mrs. Landry.

832
00:47:10.578 --> 00:47:12.547
You figured it out.

833
00:47:13.438 --> 00:47:15.000
Yeah.

834
00:47:15.413 --> 00:47:18.353
But I really.
really Don't wanna do it.

835
00:47:18.850 --> 00:47:20.592
[Indistinct conversations]

836
00:47:24.235 --> 00:47:25.865
[Door closes]

837
00:47:27.143 --> 00:47:28.460
Hi.

838
00:47:30.780 --> 00:47:32.467
Hello! Hi there.

839
00:47:32.538 --> 00:47:33.538
- Jimmy!
- Jimmy.

840
00:47:33.617 --> 00:47:34.710
Jimmy.

841
00:47:34.786 --> 00:47:36.986
Okeydokey.

842
00:47:42.324 --> 00:47:44.393
Testing.
Testing.

843
00:47:44.394 --> 00:47:46.729
Good morning.
All: Good morning.

844
00:47:46.730 --> 00:47:49.850
I know that many of you
were expecting Sandy

845
00:47:49.920 --> 00:47:52.866
for this morning's chair yoga.
but her daughter has a cold.

846
00:47:52.975 --> 00:47:54.487
[All groan]
But she'll be fine.

847
00:47:54.535 --> 00:47:57.850
Uh. the nice folks in front
said I could sit in.

848
00:47:57.936 --> 00:48:00.036
So. you guys ready to get to it?

849
00:48:00.084 --> 00:48:01.202
(All:) Yes.

850
00:48:01.250 --> 00:48:02.631
[Chuckling] Okay.

851
00:48:02.725 --> 00:48:07.444
Let's wake up those spines with.
uh. cat/cow position.

852
00:48:07.818 --> 00:48:09.389
[Clears throat]
Very good.

853
00:48:09.447 --> 00:48:10.514
Cat...

854
00:48:10.687 --> 00:48:12.397
[Exhales deeply]

855
00:48:12.527 --> 00:48:14.495
And then cow...

856
00:48:14.620 --> 00:48:17.249
[Inhales deeply]

857
00:48:17.459 --> 00:48:19.694
Sit up straight.
Very good. Jasper.

858
00:48:19.800 --> 00:48:21.663
Cat...
[Exhales deeply]

859
00:48:22.131 --> 00:48:24.194
And cow...
[Inhales deeply]

860
00:48:24.565 --> 00:48:25.874
Long. deep breaths.

861
00:48:25.922 --> 00:48:28.858
Breathe in through the nose
and out through the mouth.

862
00:48:29.108 --> 00:48:30.874
[Exhales deeply]

863
00:48:31.059 --> 00:48:32.389
And cow...

864
00:48:32.542 --> 00:48:34.661
[Inhales deeply]

865
00:48:35.070 --> 00:48:37.083
And cat...

866
00:48:37.401 --> 00:48:38.967
[Exhales deeply]

867
00:48:39.034 --> 00:48:40.934
Mr. McGill.
[Door closes]

868
00:48:41.037 --> 00:48:42.304
Erin Brill!

869
00:48:42.352 --> 00:48:44.920
You're just in time
for chair yoga.

870
00:48:45.038 --> 00:48:48.350
- [Exhales deeply]
- I need to talk to you.

871
00:48:48.758 --> 00:48:50.579
Uh. well. pull up a chair.

872
00:48:50.672 --> 00:48:52.482
There's always room
for one more.

873
00:48:52.654 --> 00:48:54.420
- [Exhales deeply]
- Now. Mr. McGill.

874
00:48:54.557 --> 00:48:56.557
[Inhales deeply]

875
00:49:02.638 --> 00:49:04.787
- What?
- You are unbelievable.

876
00:49:04.875 --> 00:49:07.563
I could not. for the life of me.
figure out why on earth

877
00:49:07.611 --> 00:49:09.633
Mrs. Landry would suddenly
change her mind

878
00:49:09.681 --> 00:49:11.409
about the sandpiper settlement.

879
00:49:11.414 --> 00:49:14.155
I had to practically drag
the information out of her

880
00:49:14.203 --> 00:49:15.347
that you filled her head

881
00:49:15.406 --> 00:49:16.950
and all of her friends' heads
with lies.

882
00:49:16.997 --> 00:49:18.530
I never lied to anyone.

883
00:49:18.688 --> 00:49:22.188
You drastically misrepresented
the reality of the case.

884
00:49:22.443 --> 00:49:23.643
So?

885
00:49:23.793 --> 00:49:25.102
So?!

886
00:49:25.538 --> 00:49:27.861
You took advantage
of poor Mrs. Landry.

887
00:49:28.078 --> 00:49:30.125
<i>Does she know how much money
you're gonna make from this?</i>

888
00:49:30.172 --> 00:49:33.477
<i>Nope.
And again I ask... so what?</i>

889
00:49:33.603 --> 00:49:35.195
<i>These people trusted you. Jimmy.</i>

890
00:49:35.249 --> 00:49:38.309
<i>Do you have any idea
how much time I had to put in</i>

891
00:49:38.506 --> 00:49:41.703
<i>listening to their insipid
ramblings about their sciatica</i>

892
00:49:41.751 --> 00:49:44.151
<i>or which grandchild
disappoints them the most?</i>

893
00:49:44.315 --> 00:49:45.982
Damn right they trust me.

894
00:49:46.108 --> 00:49:48.538
I worked my ass off
earning their trust.

895
00:49:48.685 --> 00:49:50.164
Then you betrayed it.

896
00:49:50.269 --> 00:49:52.883
If the only thing standing
between me and a million bucks

897
00:49:52.985 --> 00:49:54.172
is some old lady's tears.

898
00:49:54.266 --> 00:49:56.133
then I'd suggest
investing in kleenex.

899
00:49:56.259 --> 00:49:58.460
You've ruined her life because
you wanted your money faster.

900
00:49:58.507 --> 00:50:00.203
Boo and hoo.

901
00:50:00.423 --> 00:50:04.223
Besides. it's not like she's got
that much time left. anyway.

902
00:50:04.422 --> 00:50:06.086
You're disgusting.

903
00:50:06.218 --> 00:50:07.899
And rich.

904
00:50:10.365 --> 00:50:11.835
[Sighs]

905
00:50:12.516 --> 00:50:14.188
Hey. everyone.
Apologies!

906
00:50:14.313 --> 00:50:17.391
That was probably more like
20 breaths instead of 10.

907
00:50:17.452 --> 00:50:18.765
[All murmuring]
Uh.

908
00:50:18.871 --> 00:50:22.094
I Don't see a lot of
forward folding... Going on.

909
00:50:23.089 --> 00:50:25.489
[Indistinct conversations]

910
00:50:27.898 --> 00:50:30.288
[Door opens. closes]

911
00:50:31.521 --> 00:50:32.821
[Sighs]

912
00:50:35.934 --> 00:50:37.904
Come on. girls.

913
00:50:40.026 --> 00:50:41.626
Shame on you.

914
00:50:53.497 --> 00:50:56.067
[Vehicles passing in distance]

915
00:51:02.085 --> 00:51:03.905
So?

916
00:51:04.463 --> 00:51:05.663
Like a charm. yeah.

917
00:51:05.829 --> 00:51:07.546
She'll go back
on the settlement?

918
00:51:07.690 --> 00:51:11.140
I imagine you'll hear from her
within an hour or so.

919
00:51:11.501 --> 00:51:13.249
Good.
Hey.

920
00:51:13.839 --> 00:51:15.132
Well Done in there.

921
00:51:15.519 --> 00:51:17.843
I meant every word I said.

922
00:51:19.163 --> 00:51:21.257
I know.

923
00:51:22.445 --> 00:51:23.905
Thank you.

924
00:51:27.950 --> 00:51:30.719
[Footsteps depart]

925
00:51:30.897 --> 00:51:34.020
[Car door opens. closes]

926
00:51:40.100 --> 00:51:41.715
You got the address?
Yep.

927
00:51:41.785 --> 00:51:43.710
Okay. I'll meet you guys there
in about an hour.

928
00:51:43.758 --> 00:51:45.319
- We'll unload.
- Sounds good.

929
00:51:45.535 --> 00:51:47.624
[Truck door closes]

930
00:51:48.038 --> 00:51:49.837
[Latch clinks]

931
00:51:52.386 --> 00:51:54.394
Hey.
You guys about Done?

932
00:51:54.473 --> 00:51:55.949
Yep.

933
00:51:56.468 --> 00:51:58.300
Listen. I. um...

934
00:51:58.715 --> 00:52:00.800
I'm real sorry
that this didn't work out.

935
00:52:00.848 --> 00:52:02.019
It's fine.

936
00:52:02.067 --> 00:52:04.550
I already talked to
my old supervisor at the MVD.

937
00:52:04.648 --> 00:52:06.480
Looks like
they can take me back.

938
00:52:06.528 --> 00:52:07.728
- So...
- Oh.

939
00:52:07.853 --> 00:52:09.496
That's great.
And. you know.

940
00:52:09.593 --> 00:52:14.093
if we ever get another office
up. you'd be our first call.

941
00:52:15.737 --> 00:52:18.261
Yeah.
Okay.

942
00:52:18.685 --> 00:52:20.319
Good to know.

943
00:52:21.215 --> 00:52:22.527
Bye. Kim.

944
00:52:22.651 --> 00:52:24.121
Oh. Bye.

945
00:52:37.772 --> 00:52:39.832
She understands.

946
00:52:42.358 --> 00:52:45.663
[Clicks tongue]
So. uh. what's left?

947
00:52:46.129 --> 00:52:48.264
I think this is it.
This is all admin stuff.

948
00:52:48.335 --> 00:52:51.233
Uh. appointment book.
Your rolodex.

949
00:52:54.796 --> 00:52:57.319
[Thuds]
Hey. why'd you do that?

950
00:52:57.670 --> 00:53:01.264
Because no senior's coming
within 20 feet of me ever again.

951
00:53:01.381 --> 00:53:03.878
I'm gonna need
a whole new business model

952
00:53:03.926 --> 00:53:05.483
when I get my license back.

953
00:53:05.544 --> 00:53:07.395
Kim. It's pointless.

954
00:53:07.450 --> 00:53:10.624
They're smearing my name
across the tri-state area.

955
00:53:10.686 --> 00:53:13.749
Sendin' telegrams
to everyone far and near.

956
00:53:13.936 --> 00:53:15.866
You never know.

957
00:53:18.055 --> 00:53:19.592
[Sighs]

958
00:53:24.717 --> 00:53:26.436
It's a good wall.

959
00:53:28.363 --> 00:53:29.597
You think?

960
00:53:29.739 --> 00:53:31.109
Yeah.

961
00:53:33.809 --> 00:53:35.509
We'll get another.

962
00:53:37.295 --> 00:53:39.152
A better wall.

963
00:53:41.289 --> 00:53:42.383
[Sighs]

964
00:53:42.431 --> 00:53:43.631
Ready?

965
00:53:46.178 --> 00:53:47.741
Let's go home.

966
00:53:52.135 --> 00:53:54.005
[Door creaks]

967
